{"data":[{"date":"07:20 11/07","title":"Mbappe: \"Qu\u00ean Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng \u0111i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup!\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/mbappe-quen-qua-bong-vang-di-toi-muon-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Mbappe kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a anh l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n nh\u01b0 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng.</h2><h2>Mbappe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00eam qua. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc n\u00e0y, coi nh\u01b0 Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMbappe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay. Sao tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng cho danh hi\u1ec7u Ballon d&rsquo;Or khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i teen \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau Pele ghi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup.</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mbappe m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/mbappe-quen-qua-bong-vang-di-toi-muon-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mbappe m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ebb vang tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup, Mbappe kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p thay v\u00ec ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng vinh quang cho c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u00ecnh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em>&ldquo;C\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 tin. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1eddi n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 trong gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a d\u00e1m m\u01a1 t\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd th\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111ang m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp theo ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Khi b\u1ea1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng gian l\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u00ec t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng. Khi n\u00e0o t\u00f4i c\u00f2n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup!&rdquo;.</em><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-phap-10-bi-421-190892.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1128","checkdouble":"190902"},{"date":"07:14 11/07","title":"\u201cVua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d Pele ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/pele-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-quyet-dinh-sang-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real Madrid sang Juventus. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u201cVua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb Real Madrid. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ph\u00eda Juve \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Liverpool, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Los Blancos sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/pele-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-quyet-dinh-sang-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pele c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng cho Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &ldquo;Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo; b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u cho h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Pele t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua 18 n\u0103m \u1edf Santos tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o New York Cosmos.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus-180-190857.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus-180-190857.html\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Juventus?</span><br>\r\n<span>Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Xin ch\u00fac m\u1eebng, Cristiano&rdquo;, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. &ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Santos song \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn. Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chia tay, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 15 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Real. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 4 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 5 m\u00f9a qua. Trong 9 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Los Blancos, anh ghi t\u1edbi 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 438 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e2y l\u00e0m b\u00e0n v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-nham-sao-khung-mu-thay-ronaldo-180-190887.html\">Real nh\u1eafm sao kh\u1ee7ng MU thay Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/david-trezeguet-noi-gi-ve-thuong-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-176-190885.html\">David Trezeguet n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/emre-can-hao-huc-truoc-co-hoi-choi-bong-cung-ronaldo-184-190838.html\">T\u00e2n binh Juventus h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/buffon-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-juve-chieu-mo-ronaldo-421-190836.html\">Buffon n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Juve chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1127","checkdouble":"190910"},{"date":"08:03 11/07","title":"Pogba: \"Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c th\u00f9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Euro 2016\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/croatia-tu-davor-suker-den-luca-mondric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Pogba hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup tr\u00f4i qua t\u1ea7m tay khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Euro 2016.</h2><h2>Pogba hy v\u1ecdng Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 v\u1eeba qua. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Umtiti nh\u01b0ng Pogba v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Man United l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf Euro 2016. V\u00e0 anh m\u1edbi b\u00e0y t\u1ecf hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng Les Bleus s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba hy v\u1ecdng Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pogba hy v\u1ecdng Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/croatia-tu-davor-suker-den-luca-mondric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba hy v\u1ecdng Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;L\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. H\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u01b0 Euro 2016. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Euro nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang. V\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y tr\u00f4i qua th\u00eam n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh cho tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. N\u0103m 2016, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i vui v\u00ec m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m c\u00e1c C\u0110V vui h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam 15/7 t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Pogba d\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu ni\u00ean Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t \u1edf hang Tham Luang su\u1ed1t 2 tu\u1ea7n qua. Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 13 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee9u s\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi hang \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1edf mi\u1ec1n B\u1eafc Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb ng\u1eadp cho t\u1edbi t\u1eadn th\u00e1ng 10.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch FIFA Gianni Infantino c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft th\u01b0 cho Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 m\u1eddi 12 c\u1eadu nh\u00f3c c\u00f9ng HLV t\u1edbi xem tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 ngay cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1126","checkdouble":"190911"},{"date":"08:58 11/07","title":"Eden Hazard xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T B\u1ec9 Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1edbi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</h2><h2>B\u1ec9 v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng World Cup sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n sao h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7y m\u00ea ho\u1eb7c. Ph\u00e1p nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n khi d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb B\u1ec9 b\u1eaft b\u00e0i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u01a1i l\u00e9p v\u00e9, B\u1ec9 d\u1ea7n l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi uy hi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong hi\u1ec7p 2. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. </p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phap vs Bi\" title=\"Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/boi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1eeda thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sau m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Umtiti \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 51 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o ra b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t l\u1edbn cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u1ec9 n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Eden Hazard xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p theo k\u00e8m r\u1ea5t ch\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T B\u1ec9 Eden Hazard c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng. Ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ecf ra nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi &lsquo;m\u1ea5t h\u00fat&rsquo; trong hi\u1ec7p 2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1eeba qua, Hazard th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng n\u00f3i: &ldquo;B\u1ec9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n, khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ed9i c\u00f3 hai c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 n\u00e9t, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lloris \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard\" title=\"Eden Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Eden Hazard&nbsp;xem nh\u1eb9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00eam B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i d\u00f9 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. D\u1eabu sao ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i hay nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng may \u0111\u00e3 thua m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh&rdquo;, Hazard chia s\u1ebb trong ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Hazard v\u1eabn ch\u00fac m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Anh c\u0169ng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Les Bleus s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng sau tr\u00f2n 2 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190907.html\">Thua tr\u1eadn, sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ph\u00e1p &ldquo;ph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi-469-190901.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi-469-190901.html\">HLV Deschamps khen Pogba sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nHLV Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho Paul Pogba sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u00eam qua.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tran-tranh-hang-3-cua-dt-bi-dien-ra-khi-nao-421-190898.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/tran-tranh-hang-3-cua-dt-bi-dien-ra-khi-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tran-tranh-hang-3-cua-dt-bi-dien-ra-khi-nao-421-190898.html\">Tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 di\u1ec5n ra khi n\u00e0o?</span><br>\r\nLukaku v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t &ldquo;tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng&rdquo; n\u1eefa. V\u1eady tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/Deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-dau-Phap-1-0-Bi-ban-ket-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Sau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/20180710T190939Z_500562221_UP1EE7A1H82S7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPFRBE.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1125","checkdouble":"190916"},{"date":"04:56 11/07","title":"Man City CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mahrez v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Qua \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mahrez t\u1eeb Leicester City. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a The Citizens trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u00fang ra h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 Mahrez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Man City c\u00f3 ra s\u1ee9c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u, Leicester c\u0169ng gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean quan \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Mahrez d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ee9c 95 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m Philippe Coutinho, ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1eddi Liverpool \u0111\u1ebfn Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 142 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mahrez v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mahrez v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Man-City-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-Mahrez-voi-gia-60-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mahrez v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMahrez bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Leicester d\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed9p \u0111\u01a1n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u201ch\u1ed1i h\u1eadn\u201d v\u1ec1 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed9c mua b\u00e1n di\u1ec5n ra. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p Anh, \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMahrez ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra s\u00e2n cho Leicester v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao. K\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a 2017/18, anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 10 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, gi\u00fap B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch Premier League \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 9. C\u00f2n Man City, h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 100 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00f2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"mahrez va vardy\" title=\"mahrez va vardy\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Marez l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Leicester 4 n\u0103m qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, Man City v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Mahrez c\u00f9ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Champions League. H\u1ecd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Mahrez v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1eafn \u0111o, Leicester \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. Mahrez nhanh ch\u00f3ng di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Etihad ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n y t\u1ebf b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi CLB m\u1edbi. <br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 Mahrez t\u1ea1i Leicester:</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- Mahrez gia nh\u1eadp Leicester t\u1eeb Le Havre v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 400 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng n\u0103m 2014, b\u1eb1ng 1/150 l\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Man City m\u1edbi b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 anh.<br>\r\n- Sau 179 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Leicester, Mahrez ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 48 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham (214) v\u00e0 Wilfried Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace (234) l\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 pha qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Mahrez (176) m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n- T\u1eeb khi Mahrez ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014, ch\u1ec9 8 ng\u01b0\u1eddi (Eden Hazard, Diego Costa, Eriksen, Jamie Vardy, Alexis Sanchez, Romelu Lukaku, Sergio Aguero v\u00e0 Harry Kane) l\u00e0 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-man-city-172-190593.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/toi-luot-man-city-vao-cuoc-vu-hang-hot-world-cup-2018-172-190594.html\">T\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Man City v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng hot World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-2-ben-do-tiem-nang-cua-pep-sau-khi-roi-man-city-172-190504.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! 2 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pep sau khi r\u1eddi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-sap-cong-bo-bom-tan-43-trieu-bang-172-190354.html\">Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 bom t\u1ea5n 43 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1124","checkdouble":"190895"},{"date":"05:07 11/07","title":"HLV Martinez chia s\u1ebb l\u00fd do g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/hlv-martinez-chia-se-ly-do-guc-nga-truoc-dt-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Roberto Martinez chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2>B\u1ec9 thua v\u00ec b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. H\u1ecd th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, sau pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti, qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a &ldquo;th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng&rdquo; tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, khi d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. D\u00f9 r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng HLV Roberto Martinez c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i. S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Roberto Martinez chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p\" title=\"Martinez chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/hlv-martinez-chia-se-ly-do-guc-nga-truoc-dt-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Roberto Martinez chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00f9i s\u00e2u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u, ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u00fac h\u1ecd nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Roberto Martinez chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 thua \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng World Cup 2018 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Eden Hazard v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba v\u1edbi \u0110T Croatia/Anh v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe-421-190894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe-421-190894.html\">Ferdinand tr\u00f2n m\u1eaft: L\u00e0m th\u1ebf qu\u00e1i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mbappe?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Rio Ferdinand ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 Mbappe v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd ma thu\u1eadt.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Sau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/20180710T190939Z_500562221_UP1EE7A1H82S7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPFRBE.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1123","checkdouble":"190896"},{"date":"05:20 11/07","title":"Ph\u00e1p l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup, Deschamps v\u1eabn k\u00e9m vui","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kylian Mbappe b\u00e0y tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9.\r\n</h2><h2>Mbappe l\u1ea1i \u201cl\u00e0m tr\u00f2\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi \u0110T Uruguay, sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n khi ng\u00e3 l\u0103n trong pha \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi C.Rodriguez. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Diego Godin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f2i \u201ct\u1ea9n\u201d c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, v\u00ec Mbappe h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar. Anh c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng t\u1eeb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngay sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a r\u00fat ra b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc v\u00ec b\u00e0y tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ea5u trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9. V\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng ra bi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u1eddi gian. V\u00e0 khi b\u00f3ng ra bi\u00ean v\u00e0 thu\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh che b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c r\u00ea d\u1eaft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u00e1 cay c\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u00f3i ch\u01a1i b\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a Mbappe, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1y ra x\u00f4 ng\u00e3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb. V\u00e0 ngay khi \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0103n 1 chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng t\u1eeb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. Nh\u01b0ng do FIFA x\u00f3a th\u1ebb t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1998 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau tuy\u1ec7t chi\u00eau \u0103n v\u1ea1, Mbappe b\u00e0y tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau tuy\u1ec7t chi\u00eau \u0103n v\u1ea1, Mbappe b\u00e0y tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/mbappe-tiep-tuc-de-lai-hinh-anh-cuc-xau-vi-thoi-cau-gio.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe b\u00e0y tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Kylian Mbappe b\u00e0y tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd, nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch th\u1eadm t\u1ec7. \u201cC\u1eadu ta \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng\u201d, \u201cH\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1eeb Neymar h\u01a1i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5y anh b\u1ea1n\u201d,\u2026<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng xem l\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/mbappe.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe-421-190894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe-421-190894.html\">Ferdinand tr\u00f2n m\u1eaft: L\u00e0m th\u1ebf qu\u00e1i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mbappe?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Rio Ferdinand ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 Mbappe v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd ma thu\u1eadt.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/20180710T190939Z_500562221_UP1EE7A1H82S7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPFRBE.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Sau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1122","checkdouble":"190897"},{"date":"05:29 11/07","title":"Tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 di\u1ec5n ra khi n\u00e0o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/tran-tranh-hang-3-cua-dt-bi-dien-ra-khi-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lukaku v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t \u201ctr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng\u201d n\u1eefa. V\u1eady tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra khi n\u00e0o?\r\n</h2><h2>\u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u00f2n tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng x\u00e1ch vali v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, m\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y &ndash; tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i thua trong c\u1eb7p b\u00e1n k\u1ebft 2 (Croatia ho\u1eb7c Anh). D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1eddi gian, \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay, tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h theo gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u00e0 21h gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ng\u00e0y 14/7/2018 (th\u1ee9 7 tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">SV\u0110 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Saint Petersburg v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a 65 ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0110T B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng (tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lukaku vs Phap\" title=\"Lukaku vs Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/tran-tranh-hang-3-cua-dt-bi-dien-ra-khi-nao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra khi n\u00e0o?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>L\u1ecbch s\u1eed<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Italia v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1934, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf ra. Khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u00c1o v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2014: H\u00e0 Lan 3-0 Brazil</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2010: \u0110\u1ee9c 3-2 Uruguay</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2006: \u0110\u1ee9c 3-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2002: Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 3-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1998: Croatia 2-1 H\u00e0 Lan</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1994: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 4-0 Bulgaria</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1990: \u00dd 2-1 Anh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng coi tr\u1ecdng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f3 nh\u01b0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Michel Platini trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 v\u00e0o c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup 1982 v\u00e0 1986.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f4i khi, tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 &ldquo;c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i&rdquo; \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch Brazil thua th\u1ea3m H\u00e0 Lan 0-3 t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup 2014, sau khi b\u1ecb \u0110\u1ee9c h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t 1-7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. V\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m 1974, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 Romelu Lukaku n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n, nh\u1eb1m c\u1ea1nh tranh chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng (hi\u1ec7n c\u00f2n k\u00e9m Harry Kane 2 b\u00e0n).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra khi n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190897.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190897.html\">Ph\u00e1p l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup, Deschamps v\u1eabn k\u00e9m vui</span><br>\r\nHLV Didier Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Sau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/20180710T190939Z_500562221_UP1EE7A1H82S7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPFRBE.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1121","checkdouble":"190898"},{"date":"05:51 11/07","title":"H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c B\u1ec9, Pogba gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/ha-guc-bi-pogba-gianh-chien-thang-cho-doi-bong-thai-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba tri \u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2>Pogba d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ed<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng L\u1ee3n hoang (Th\u00e1i Lan), khi 13 ng\u01b0\u1eddi bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 HLV l\u1ea1c v\u00e0o trong hang Tham Luang, t\u1ec9nh Chiang Rai. Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 10/7.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9 k\u1ebft th\u00fac th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y cho 13 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 23/6. Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram, c\u00f9ng d\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i: &ldquo;Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y g\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c anh h\u00f9ng h\u00f4m nay. L\u00e0m t\u1ed1t l\u1eafm c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft. Paul Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba tri \u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan\" title=\"Paul Pogba tri \u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/po.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paul Pogba tri \u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn, anh t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u00e2u.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, sao tr\u1ebb Kylian Mbappe c\u0169ng \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng, v\u1edbi d\u00f2ng chia s\u1ebb &ldquo;M\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi&rdquo;. 2 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a anh, Raphael Varane v\u00e0 Lucas Hernandez ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n vi\u1ebft d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef: &ldquo;Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft&rdquo;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y (01h00 ng\u00e0y 15/7), \u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft 2, gi\u1eefa \u0110T Croatia vs Anh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Paul Pogba tri \u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan, 13 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh d\u1ef1 l\u1edbn khi FIFA \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi m\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn xem tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/hau-truong/mu-moi-doi-bong-nhi-thai-lan-vua-duoc-giai-cuu-tham-san-old-trafford-188-190880.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man United c\u0169ng m\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ed \u0111\u1ebfn th\u0103m Old Trafford</span> khi h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/20180710T190939Z_500562221_UP1EE7A1H82S7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPFRBE.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span><br />\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190897.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190897.html\">Ph\u00e1p l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup, Deschamps v\u1eabn k\u00e9m vui</span><br />\r\nHLV Didier Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br />\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Sau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1120","checkdouble":"190899"},{"date":"06:22 11/07","title":"Sau tuy\u1ec7t chi\u00eau \u0103n v\u1ea1, Mbappe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ef1c x\u1ea5u v\u00ec th\u00f3i c\u00e2u gi\u1edd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/mbappe-tiep-tuc-de-lai-hinh-anh-cuc-xau-vi-thoi-cau-gio.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kylian Mbappe b\u00e0y tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9.\r\n</h2><h2>Mbappe l\u1ea1i \u201cl\u00e0m tr\u00f2\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi \u0110T Uruguay, sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n khi ng\u00e3 l\u0103n trong pha \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi C.Rodriguez. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Diego Godin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f2i \u201ct\u1ea9n\u201d c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, v\u00ec Mbappe h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar. Anh c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng t\u1eeb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngay sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a r\u00fat ra b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc v\u00ec b\u00e0y tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ea5u trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9. V\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng ra bi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u1eddi gian. V\u00e0 khi b\u00f3ng ra bi\u00ean v\u00e0 thu\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh che b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c r\u00ea d\u1eaft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u00e1 cay c\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u00f3i ch\u01a1i b\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a Mbappe, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1y ra x\u00f4 ng\u00e3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb. V\u00e0 ngay khi \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0103n 1 chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng t\u1eeb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. Nh\u01b0ng do FIFA x\u00f3a th\u1ebb t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1998 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau tuy\u1ec7t chi\u00eau \u0103n v\u1ea1, Mbappe b\u00e0y tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau tuy\u1ec7t chi\u00eau \u0103n v\u1ea1, Mbappe b\u00e0y tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/mbappe-tiep-tuc-de-lai-hinh-anh-cuc-xau-vi-thoi-cau-gio.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe b\u00e0y tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Kylian Mbappe b\u00e0y tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd, nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch th\u1eadm t\u1ec7. \u201cC\u1eadu ta \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng\u201d, \u201cH\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1eeb Neymar h\u01a1i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5y anh b\u1ea1n\u201d,\u2026<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng xem l\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/mbappe.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe-421-190894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe-421-190894.html\">Ferdinand tr\u00f2n m\u1eaft: L\u00e0m th\u1ebf qu\u00e1i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mbappe?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Rio Ferdinand ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 Mbappe v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd ma thu\u1eadt.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/20180710T190939Z_500562221_UP1EE7A1H82S7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPFRBE.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Sau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1119","checkdouble":"190900"},{"date":"06:32 11/07","title":"HLV Deschamps khen Pogba sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho Paul Pogba sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u00eam qua.</h2><h2>Deschamps khen Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Samuel Umtiti l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 \u1edf ph\u00fat 51. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u00e0 s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa Croatia v\u00e0 Anh k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPogba kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p. Nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi t\u1ea1i St. Petersburg. Pogba t\u1ea1o ra 3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra 4 pha t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Deschamps khen Pogba sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Deschamps khen Pogba sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Deschamps khen Pogba sau tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Didier Deschamps sau tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc t\u00ean nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 Pogba g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t kh\u1eafp m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 HLV Martinez \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Fellaini k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p ri\u00eang Pogba. C\u0169ng v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 Pogba \u00edt khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 do ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c th\u1eeba n\u1eefa. Pogba thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPogba \u0111ang d\u1ea7n th\u00edch nghi h\u01a1n v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y hay th\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec. V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 t\u0103ng th\u00eam t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 n\u00e0y h\u01a1n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Deschamps mu\u1ed1n vi\u1ebft trang s\u1eed m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 20 n\u0103m, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng quang danh hi\u1ec7u World Cup khi Deschamps l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng. V\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a Les Bleus hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng so s\u00e1nh m\u00e0 mong r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd vi\u1ebft n\u00ean trang s\u1eed m\u1edbi cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1ed1ng \u1edf th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u0110\u1eebng bao gi\u1edd n\u00f3i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd v\u1ec1 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ed3i. M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a sinh ra v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh. Vinh quang \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng so s\u00e1nh. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 20 n\u0103m, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 10 n\u0103m. T\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi h\u1ecd h\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean trang s\u1eed m\u1edbi, trang s\u1eed \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Ph\u00e1p:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1118","checkdouble":"190901"},{"date":"06:27 11/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (11/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1172018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 11/7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\