0y tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/Deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-dau-Phap-1-0-Bi-ban-ket-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br />\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Sau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/20180710T190939Z_500562221_UP1EE7A1H82S7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPFRBE.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span><br />\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1116","checkdouble":"190905"},{"date":"06:51 11/07","title":"Thua tr\u1eadn, sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ph\u00e1p \u201cph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u201cph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSu\u1ed1t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2018 t\u1edbi nay, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00ednh th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p trong tay c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, HLV Didier Deschamps v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00e1p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng, \u0111\u1eb7t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 n\u01a1i ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Antoine Griezmann hay Kylian Mbappe c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nhanh nh\u1eb9n, Les Blues ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Thibaut-Courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Phap-1-0-Bi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p l\u1ea1i t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Griezmann gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y, s\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 h\u01a1n. Sau c\u00f9ng, h\u1ecd khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois b\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u201cph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. \u201cPh\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1eed t\u1ebf\u201d, Courtois n\u00f3i v\u1edbi h\u00e3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Sporza c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Courtois\" title=\"thu mon Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ee9c x\u00fac</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ch\u01a1i theo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. H\u1ecd ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThua tr\u1eadn, B\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a Courtois s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i thua trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft 2 gi\u1eefa Croatia v\u00e0 Anh v\u00e0o 21h ng\u00e0y 14/7 t\u1edbi. C\u00f2n Ph\u00e1p b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra 22h ng\u00e0y 15/7 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-vao-chung-ket-nguoi-dan-paris-do-ra-duong-di-bao-421-190905.html\">Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Paris \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i b\u00e3o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi-469-190901.html\">HLV Deschamps khen Pogba sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190897.html\">Ph\u00e1p l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup, Deschamps v\u1eabn k\u00e9m vui</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe-421-190894.html\">Ferdinand tr\u00f2n m\u1eaft: L\u00e0m th\u1ebf qu\u00e1i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mbappe?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-phap-10-bi-421-190892.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1115","checkdouble":"190907"},{"date":"16:02 10/07","title":"Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Juventus?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">4-3-1-2 v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/lo-so-ao-cua-ronaldo-o-juventus-180-190540.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span>, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 31 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t vui v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh CR7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus Allegri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus Allegri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Cristiano-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-Allegri-co-the-van-hanh-so-do-nao-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-3-1-2 v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u1ebfu Ronaldo h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi Higuain. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft nhau r\u1ea5t r\u00f5, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i kho\u1ea3ng 80 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi nhau. Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain l\u00e0 2 trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, HLV Massimiliano Allegri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 4-3-1-2 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Matuidi, Pjanic v\u00e0 Can l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. Dybala ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDybala l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdc khe c\u1ee7a anh mang \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n hai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u0169ng gi\u00fap anh ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4-3-3 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Higuain, Dybala v\u00e0 Mandzukic l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. Khi Mandzukic kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n th\u00ec Douglas Costa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4-3-3 voi bo ba tan cong Ronaldo, Higuain va Dybala\" title=\"4-3-3 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-3-3 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1edbi 3 m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Juventus mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u00e1t huy nhi\u1ec1u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng g\u1ed3m 3 m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean nhau. CR7 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, Dybala ch\u01a1i c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n Higuain ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ee7ng&nbsp;khi\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Juventus c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean gia l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Pjanic, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Emre Can v\u00e0 Blaise Matuidi \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, Juventus c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng khi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o CR7. Khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Higuain v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Juventus s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, khi \u0111\u00f3 anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4-2-3-1 voi Ronaldo da cao nhat tren hang cong\" title=\"4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/3.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus, HLV Allegri kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng b\u1edfi Ronaldo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi CR7 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a Dybala t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau, Ronaldo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 18 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Higuain nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Ronaldo thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Higuain, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Dybala \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. V\u1edbi Douglas Costa v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Dybala, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng v\u0169 kh\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4-3-3 v\u1edbi Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus ho\u1eb7c HLV Allegri kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 v\u1edbi Paulo Dybala, Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa l\u00e0 3 m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4-3-3 voi Dybala, Ronaldo va Douglas Costa tren hang cong\" title=\"4-3-3 v\u1edbi Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/4.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-3-3 v\u1edbi Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong, Dybala v\u00e0 Douglas Costa ch\u01a1i \u1edf hai c\u00e1nh. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 CR7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 t\u1ed1t th\u00ec t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Dybala v\u00e0 Douglas Costa, s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa b\u1ed9 ba n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMiralem Pjanic s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia c\u0169ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdc khe s\u1eafc l\u1eb9m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 thi\u00ean t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Juventus&nbsp;mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1114","checkdouble":"190857"}]}